public class RptVertex
extends edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.impl.DirectedSparseVertex

A vertex is the JUNG counterpart of a node on the RPT. Contains extra info, such as the distribution of labels, whether it comes from a YES/NO branch, and whether it's a leaf or not.
